1
00:00:13,010 --> 00:00:15,810
[Episode 2]

2
00:00:21,334 --> 00:00:21,933
Steward Xu,

3
00:00:22,174 --> 00:00:23,653
did you hear footsteps over there?

4
00:00:24,574 --> 00:00:25,293
Where?

5
00:00:25,734 --> 00:00:27,213
Coming from the Second Young Master's room.

6
00:00:27,934 --> 00:00:28,453
Let's go.

7
00:00:28,454 --> 00:00:28,973
Yes.

8
00:00:41,534 --> 00:00:42,733
I have to take a chance.

9
00:00:47,934 --> 00:00:48,893
It's raining.

10
00:00:59,734 --> 00:01:00,573
Concubine.

11
00:01:01,374 --> 00:01:01,853
How did you...

12
00:01:01,854 --> 00:01:02,453
Second Young Master.

13
00:01:03,974 --> 00:01:04,733
Help me.

14
00:01:05,134 --> 00:01:05,653
Second Young Master.

15
00:01:06,454 --> 00:01:08,293
We just heard some noises from your room.

16
00:01:08,414 --> 00:01:09,373
Is everything alright?

17
00:01:15,254 --> 00:01:15,973
Everything's fine.

18
00:01:17,254 --> 00:01:18,653
A stray cat trying to escape the rain

19
00:01:19,454 --> 00:01:20,573
darted in here, that's all.

20
00:01:21,734 --> 00:01:22,373
Young Master,

21
00:01:22,454 --> 00:01:23,933
should we go in and deal with it?

22
00:01:24,374 --> 00:01:25,533
It's just a kitten.

23
00:01:26,014 --> 00:01:26,973
It looks pitiful.

24
00:01:31,174 --> 00:01:32,293
If there's nothing else,

25
00:01:32,534 --> 00:01:33,853
I'll go patrol the area.

26
00:01:34,294 --> 00:01:35,373
Thank you for your work.

27
00:01:42,334 --> 00:01:43,333
Thank you for earlier.

28
00:01:43,974 --> 00:01:44,893
I'll leave now.

29
00:01:45,014 --> 00:01:46,653
Aren't you going to explain?

30
00:01:52,174 --> 00:01:54,333
I was searching for a lost personal item

31
00:01:55,174 --> 00:01:55,893
and accidentally

32
00:01:56,294 --> 00:01:57,013
went to the backyard.

33
00:01:57,734 --> 00:01:59,133
There, I encountered something spooky.

34
00:01:59,614 --> 00:02:01,213
I got scared and came back.

35
00:02:01,894 --> 00:02:02,653
But...

36
00:02:02,734 --> 00:02:03,453
I was afraid they'd think

37
00:02:03,774 --> 00:02:05,413
I was the one pretending to be a ghost.

38
00:02:06,454 --> 00:02:08,293
So I had to hide here with you.

39
00:02:08,654 --> 00:02:09,533
But, Concubine,

40
00:02:09,774 --> 00:02:10,893
why do you think

41
00:02:11,414 --> 00:02:12,293
I would believe you?

42
00:02:16,334 --> 00:02:17,213
In the entire Zhou residence,

43
00:02:18,534 --> 00:02:20,773
you seem the most kind and reliable.

44
00:02:22,214 --> 00:02:22,893
Is that so?

45
00:02:26,014 --> 00:02:27,213
They just left.

46
00:02:27,774 --> 00:02:28,573
You should go now.

47
00:02:31,174 --> 00:02:31,653
Wait.

48
00:02:38,654 --> 00:02:39,853
The wound on your neck...

49
00:02:42,294 --> 00:02:44,813
I got scratched by bamboo outside when I came in.

50
00:02:46,814 --> 00:02:48,253
I'll get medicine for you.

51
00:02:50,734 --> 00:02:52,333
This was a gift from my foreign language tutor.

52
00:02:52,574 --> 00:02:53,333
It works very well.

53
00:02:53,774 --> 00:02:54,653
Just one night,

54
00:02:55,174 --> 00:02:55,773
and tomorrow,

55
00:02:55,854 --> 00:02:56,973
it will heal without a trace.

56
00:03:00,494 --> 00:03:01,253
It's inconvenient.

57
00:03:01,574 --> 00:03:02,933
for me to take it back.

58
00:03:03,614 --> 00:03:05,213
Could you apply it for me?

59
00:03:11,854 --> 00:03:13,093
Then I'll apply it for you.

60
00:03:21,214 --> 00:03:21,853
Does it hurt?

61
00:03:22,414 --> 00:03:23,573
This medicine contains alcohol.

62
00:03:24,174 --> 00:03:24,973
Bear with it.

63
00:03:28,294 --> 00:03:30,093
When I was hiding under the desk earlier,

64
00:03:31,014 --> 00:03:32,773
I caught a glimpse of some carvings.

65
00:03:33,174 --> 00:03:34,453
Are they your work?

66
00:03:39,774 --> 00:03:41,293
Please don't tell Father.

67
00:03:41,774 --> 00:03:43,093
I'll discard them immediately.

68
00:03:43,334 --> 00:03:44,413
Why discard them?

69
00:03:44,774 --> 00:03:46,413
I think they're carved quite well.

70
00:03:46,614 --> 00:03:47,613
To my parents,

71
00:03:48,294 --> 00:03:50,333
those are just worthless trash.

72
00:03:50,974 --> 00:03:51,653
There's no need

73
00:03:51,654 --> 00:03:53,173
to be harsh on yourself

74
00:03:53,174 --> 00:03:54,213
to meet others' expectations.

75
00:03:55,454 --> 00:03:57,013
Not only will I not tell anyone,

76
00:03:57,894 --> 00:03:58,853
but I'm really looking forward

77
00:03:59,174 --> 00:04:00,293
to your next work.

78
00:04:02,214 --> 00:04:02,933
The medicine is applied.

79
00:04:18,574 --> 00:04:20,853
How could wood carving be an unworthy pursuit?

80
00:04:21,374 --> 00:04:22,973
From tables and chairs we use, to the beds

81
00:04:22,974 --> 00:04:24,693
and the intricate carvings on cabinets...

82
00:04:25,814 --> 00:04:26,453
If I had

83
00:04:26,454 --> 00:04:28,253
your remarkable skills,

84
00:04:28,254 --> 00:04:29,813
I wouldn't need to work in the mansion.

85
00:04:30,134 --> 00:04:31,733
To have something you love doing

86
00:04:32,254 --> 00:04:33,253
and excel at it.

87
00:04:33,614 --> 00:04:34,693
You're truly impressive.

88
00:04:34,974 --> 00:04:36,253
I genuinely admire you.

89
00:04:37,494 --> 00:04:38,253
Rest assured,

90
00:04:38,374 --> 00:04:39,973
I'll keep your secret safe.

91
00:05:15,894 --> 00:05:16,893
You again!

92
00:05:19,014 --> 00:05:20,253
You finally returned.

93
00:05:20,414 --> 00:05:21,413
I've been waiting for you.

94
00:05:23,334 --> 00:05:24,773
Why are you in my room in the middle of the night?

95
00:05:24,774 --> 00:05:25,853
Delivering medicine.

96
00:05:27,774 --> 00:05:29,013
Aren't you injured?

97
00:05:29,654 --> 00:05:31,293
Pity on you.

98
00:05:31,614 --> 00:05:32,893
You came to my room

99
00:05:33,414 --> 00:05:35,013
just to deliver medicine?

100
00:05:35,454 --> 00:05:36,173
What else?

101
00:05:37,254 --> 00:05:38,413
On your wedding night,

102
00:05:38,854 --> 00:05:40,093
what do you want me

103
00:05:40,094 --> 00:05:40,933
to do with you?

104
00:05:42,014 --> 00:05:42,893
Fifth Concubine.

105
00:05:43,534 --> 00:05:45,013
Master sent me to find you.

106
00:05:45,414 --> 00:05:46,413
Are you asleep?

107
00:05:47,774 --> 00:05:48,613
Open the door.

108
00:05:49,334 --> 00:05:50,293
Feeling guilty?

109
00:05:50,774 --> 00:05:51,613
Fifth Concubine.

110
00:05:51,854 --> 00:05:52,653
Are you there?

111
00:05:53,254 --> 00:05:54,733
You're the one who should feel guilty.

112
00:05:55,294 --> 00:05:56,893
If you don't open the door,

113
00:05:56,934 --> 00:05:58,693
how else could I get in?

114
00:05:59,294 --> 00:06:00,653
We're accomplices now.

115
00:06:04,374 --> 00:06:05,373
Stay in bed,

116
00:06:05,854 --> 00:06:06,733
don't go anywhere.

117
00:06:06,854 --> 00:06:07,933
Okay.

118
00:06:15,774 --> 00:06:16,613
Come in.

119
00:06:20,614 --> 00:06:21,493
It's so late.

120
00:06:21,574 --> 00:06:22,973
What brings you here, Steward Xu?

121
00:06:23,174 --> 00:06:24,293
I've already retired for the night.

122
00:06:25,014 --> 00:06:25,853
Master instructed me

123
00:06:25,894 --> 00:06:27,133
to deliver medicine to you.

124
00:06:30,694 --> 00:06:31,493
Thank you.

125
00:06:32,374 --> 00:06:32,893
By the way,

126
00:06:33,294 --> 00:06:35,013
I heard some commotion outside earlier.

127
00:06:35,014 --> 00:06:36,133
Did something happen?

128
00:06:37,014 --> 00:06:38,453
Probably just shadows in the dark,

129
00:06:38,654 --> 00:06:39,853
you mistook them.

130
00:06:39,934 --> 00:06:40,853
Got frightened.

131
00:06:41,534 --> 00:06:42,293
Rest assured,

132
00:06:42,654 --> 00:06:43,773
I've specially increased patrols

133
00:06:43,814 --> 00:06:44,693
around the courtyard.

134
00:06:44,774 --> 00:06:45,613
Perfectly safe.

135
00:06:47,334 --> 00:06:48,093
Good that nothing's wrong.

136
00:06:48,934 --> 00:06:50,093
We'll take our leave now.

137
00:07:07,334 --> 00:07:08,093
Speak.

138
00:07:08,374 --> 00:07:09,693
Where did this jade pendant come from?

139
00:07:10,214 --> 00:07:12,373
He must have seen my sister's pendant.

140
00:07:13,894 --> 00:07:15,693
I got this pair of pendants

141
00:07:15,694 --> 00:07:17,213
from Granny at the flea market.

142
00:07:17,334 --> 00:07:18,893
Nothing valuable.

143
00:07:20,294 --> 00:07:22,333
I deeply admire the two lines

144
00:07:22,774 --> 00:07:24,173
of Nüshu inscribed upon it.

145
00:07:24,574 --> 00:07:25,893
We each kept one

146
00:07:25,934 --> 00:07:27,093
to inspire ourselves.

147
00:07:29,494 --> 00:07:31,133
Right: My life is to please myself.

148
00:07:31,654 --> 00:07:33,573
Left: Our birthright is liberty.

149
00:07:35,654 --> 00:07:37,253
He already suspects my identity.

150
00:07:37,534 --> 00:07:39,253
It couldn't be just about delivering medicine.

151
00:07:39,814 --> 00:07:42,133
The haunting must be related to him.

152
00:07:42,694 --> 00:07:44,133
But the second concubine is his mother.

153
00:07:44,614 --> 00:07:46,173
What exactly is he trying to do?

154
00:07:49,694 --> 00:07:50,253
Father.

155
00:07:50,894 --> 00:07:52,013
Mother made this herself.

156
00:07:52,534 --> 00:07:53,333
She remembered

157
00:07:53,534 --> 00:07:54,493
how you often mentioned

158
00:07:54,494 --> 00:07:55,573
the peach blossom pastry from home.

159
00:07:55,814 --> 00:07:56,493
So today, Mother...

160
00:07:56,494 --> 00:07:56,933
Just leave it there.

161
00:07:57,094 --> 00:07:57,733
No appetite.

162
00:08:00,014 --> 00:08:00,693
Master.

163
00:08:01,334 --> 00:08:03,493
Second concubine reminds you to take your medicine on time...

164
00:08:08,494 --> 00:08:09,013
By the way,

165
00:08:10,294 --> 00:08:10,933
I heard

166
00:08:11,094 --> 00:08:12,893
she saw a ghost last night.

167
00:08:13,174 --> 00:08:14,293
What exactly happened?

168
00:08:15,174 --> 00:08:16,533
We've searched the entire manor.

169
00:08:16,574 --> 00:08:17,973
Nothing unusual was found.

170
00:08:18,334 --> 00:08:18,853
I think

171
00:08:18,854 --> 00:08:20,573
she must have mistaken something she saw.

172
00:08:24,454 --> 00:08:26,253
That's good then.

173
00:08:27,134 --> 00:08:28,853
Find a fortune teller to come take a look.

174
00:08:28,974 --> 00:08:30,013
To ward off evil spirits.

175
00:08:30,254 --> 00:08:31,533
I'll also find time to accompany her.

176
00:08:31,894 --> 00:08:33,653
I have indeed neglected her lately.

177
00:08:34,974 --> 00:08:36,333
Her jealousy

178
00:08:37,174 --> 00:08:38,693
must have flared up long ago.

179
00:08:41,854 --> 00:08:42,573
Master.

180
00:08:53,894 --> 00:08:55,893
Greetings, Master.

181
00:08:57,014 --> 00:08:58,093
Greetings, Second Young Master.

182
00:09:00,854 --> 00:09:01,613
Fifth concubine.

183
00:09:02,014 --> 00:09:03,173
Your dress

184
00:09:03,174 --> 00:09:04,613
is truly elegant and refined.

185
00:09:05,294 --> 00:09:05,853
Beautiful.

186
00:09:06,454 --> 00:09:07,333
Come, come over.

187
00:09:09,974 --> 00:09:12,573
This fabric isn't particularly expensive,

188
00:09:12,574 --> 00:09:13,933
I made it all myself.

189
00:09:16,414 --> 00:09:18,253
What skillful hands you have!

190
00:09:22,934 --> 00:09:24,333
Master, I beg for justice!

191
00:09:24,614 --> 00:09:25,973
This bitch tried to kill me!

192
00:09:33,134 --> 00:09:33,773
Wangshu,

193
00:09:33,774 --> 00:09:34,733
what are you doing?

194
00:09:34,974 --> 00:09:35,693
Master,

195
00:09:36,454 --> 00:09:38,253
do you know who pretended to be a ghost to harm me?

196
00:09:39,374 --> 00:09:40,173
It was her!

197
00:09:40,854 --> 00:09:42,853
I almost died yesterday!

198
00:09:45,494 --> 00:09:46,253
Second concubine,

199
00:09:46,534 --> 00:09:47,413
accusations require proof.

200
00:09:47,734 --> 00:09:48,413
In all matters,

201
00:09:48,614 --> 00:09:50,013
we must rely on evidence.

202
00:09:51,974 --> 00:09:53,293
I do have evidence.

203
00:09:53,894 --> 00:09:54,533
This was found

204
00:09:54,534 --> 00:09:56,013
last night in the backyard pond.

205
00:09:56,254 --> 00:09:57,493
Her personal sachet.

206
00:09:57,774 --> 00:09:59,333
Her name is embroidered on it.

207
00:10:06,774 --> 00:10:08,213
You're framing me!

208
00:10:08,974 --> 00:10:10,013
So what if I am?

209
00:10:10,974 --> 00:10:12,693
[Zhiqiu]

210
00:10:13,134 --> 00:10:13,853
Fifth concubine,

211
00:10:14,534 --> 00:10:15,813
what exactly is going on?

212
00:10:19,854 --> 00:10:22,133
After leaving your room last night,

213
00:10:22,374 --> 00:10:23,653
I stayed in my own room

214
00:10:23,894 --> 00:10:24,933
and never went out.

215
00:10:25,494 --> 00:10:26,893
I only learned of this matter

216
00:10:26,974 --> 00:10:28,133
when the steward brought me medicine.

217
00:10:28,614 --> 00:10:29,773
As for this sachet,

218
00:10:30,014 --> 00:10:31,373
is it possible

219
00:10:31,454 --> 00:10:32,493
someone prepared it in advance

220
00:10:32,494 --> 00:10:33,693
to frame me?

221
00:10:34,094 --> 00:10:34,973
Master,

222
00:10:35,294 --> 00:10:36,533
please uncover the truth.

223
00:10:37,134 --> 00:10:38,453
If Fifth concubine was pretending

224
00:10:38,814 --> 00:10:40,333
to be a ghost in the pond last night,

225
00:10:40,534 --> 00:10:41,773
her hair should be damp.

226
00:10:41,934 --> 00:10:43,333
The steward visited her room.

227
00:10:43,454 --> 00:10:45,173
We'll know if her hair was wet by asking.

228
00:10:45,654 --> 00:10:46,373
Master,

229
00:10:46,494 --> 00:10:47,813
Fifth Concubine's hair

230
00:10:47,814 --> 00:10:49,133
was indeed wet last night.

231
00:10:49,294 --> 00:10:49,773
See?

232
00:10:50,214 --> 00:10:51,213
It matches.

233
00:10:51,294 --> 00:10:52,573
When the steward patrolled last night,

234
00:10:53,214 --> 00:10:54,333
I had just finished washing up.

235
00:10:54,894 --> 00:10:55,973
My hair hadn't dried yet.

236
00:10:56,774 --> 00:10:58,573
My hair being wet

237
00:10:58,814 --> 00:11:00,333
doesn't prove I went outside

238
00:11:00,574 --> 00:11:01,813
or visited the backyard.

239
00:11:03,694 --> 00:11:04,413
Fifth concubine!

240
00:11:29,814 --> 00:11:31,773
Fifth concubine, get up.

241
00:11:35,374 --> 00:11:35,853
Chen,

242
00:11:36,534 --> 00:11:38,893
find the best tailor in Wu County tomorrow,

243
00:11:39,094 --> 00:11:40,293
select the finest fabrics,

244
00:11:40,614 --> 00:11:41,533
and have fifth concubine

245
00:11:42,214 --> 00:11:43,453
tailor several nice outfits.

246
00:11:44,734 --> 00:11:45,573
Yes, Father.

247
00:11:46,654 --> 00:11:47,253
Fifth concubine,

248
00:11:47,894 --> 00:11:48,573
from now on,

249
00:11:49,134 --> 00:11:51,133
stop making your own clothes, okay?

250
00:11:53,094 --> 00:11:53,773
Dad,

251
00:11:54,694 --> 00:11:57,133
with the bats and ghosts yesterday...

252
00:12:00,414 --> 00:12:02,613
She may not ward off evil spirits well.

253
00:12:11,094 --> 00:12:11,733
Master,

254
00:12:12,654 --> 00:12:13,453
I

255
00:12:14,934 --> 00:12:16,613
finally have a home.

256
00:12:17,934 --> 00:12:18,893
I beg you, Master

257
00:12:19,894 --> 00:12:21,093
don't drive me away.

258
00:12:28,534 --> 00:12:29,373
Fifth concubine,

259
00:12:29,894 --> 00:12:31,773
you'll be confined to the side chamber.

260
00:12:32,134 --> 00:12:33,573
After I consult a fortune teller,

261
00:12:33,574 --> 00:12:34,573
we'll decide.

262
00:12:39,894 --> 00:12:40,613
Master!

263
00:12:46,974 --> 00:12:47,733
Fifth Concubine,

264
00:12:48,214 --> 00:12:48,853
this way.

265
00:13:43,614 --> 00:13:44,613
Are you going out for a date

266
00:13:45,094 --> 00:13:46,573
in the middle of the night?

267
00:13:52,214 --> 00:13:53,213
Why are you here?

268
00:13:53,854 --> 00:13:55,733
Daring to barge in while confined?

269
00:13:56,694 --> 00:13:57,813
Aren't you afraid of being seen?

270
00:13:57,814 --> 00:13:58,693
Afraid of being seen?

271
00:13:59,694 --> 00:14:00,613
Then scream.

272
00:14:01,294 --> 00:14:02,573
They'll come rescue you.

273
00:14:08,214 --> 00:14:08,933
Why seek me?

274
00:14:12,174 --> 00:14:13,693
That's my question for you.

275
00:14:15,254 --> 00:14:16,773
Last night you entered my room,

276
00:14:16,774 --> 00:14:18,293
stole my personal sachet,

277
00:14:18,414 --> 00:14:19,893
and then framed me

278
00:14:19,894 --> 00:14:21,413
for the pond haunting.

279
00:14:21,774 --> 00:14:22,413
Young Master,

280
00:14:23,334 --> 00:14:24,813
why do this?

281
00:14:25,934 --> 00:14:26,693
Why?

282
00:14:27,534 --> 00:14:30,013
To make you leave Zhou Manor sooner.

283
00:14:30,454 --> 00:14:31,413
Leave now,

284
00:14:31,574 --> 00:14:32,733
and I'll leave you with a whole body.

285
00:14:32,734 --> 00:14:34,333
So now you admit

286
00:14:34,934 --> 00:14:35,853
the pond haunting

287
00:14:35,854 --> 00:14:37,213
is connected to you.

288
00:14:37,214 --> 00:14:38,573
You hired the female ghost!

289
00:14:38,574 --> 00:14:39,853
Didn't you go to the pond too?

290
00:14:45,454 --> 00:14:47,293
Are you going to give me a shave?

291
00:14:48,174 --> 00:14:49,693
Beard doesn't grow on the neck.

292
00:14:50,094 --> 00:14:52,173
You don't know me...

293
00:14:52,534 --> 00:14:54,093
Then let me get to know you better.

294
00:14:54,534 --> 00:14:55,733
I don't mind doing it here.

295
00:15:00,094 --> 00:15:00,733
I'm

296
00:15:02,294 --> 00:15:04,853
determined to stay in Zhou Manor.

297
00:15:06,694 --> 00:15:07,733
If you make me leave,

298
00:15:09,294 --> 00:15:10,693
I'll take you down with me.

299
00:15:11,854 --> 00:15:13,013
If you want me dead,

300
00:15:14,734 --> 00:15:16,093
I'll make sure you die with me.

301
00:15:17,414 --> 00:15:18,813
No one in this manor

302
00:15:20,414 --> 00:15:22,213
is easy to deal with.

303
00:15:22,934 --> 00:15:24,413
You can't win against them.

304
00:15:28,014 --> 00:15:29,453
Why should I fight them?

305
00:15:31,214 --> 00:15:33,213
I don't mind sharing

306
00:15:34,934 --> 00:15:35,613
